{"title":"DIY Loose Leaf System","slug":"diy-loose-leaf-system","date":"2012-09-07T08:58:34.000Z","updated":"2018-04-21T08:18:25.482Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/diy-loose-leaf-system.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"用个人订制的活页来进行日程管理、流程规划与改进。","covers":null,"content":"<p>用个人订制的活页来进行日程管理、流程规划与改进。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h2 id=\"Calendar-To-do-list-and-Schedule\"><a href=\"#Calendar-To-do-list-and-Schedule\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Calendar, To-do list and Schedule\"></a>Calendar, To-do list and Schedule</h2><p>Current Daily Planner Project in <a href=\"https://github.com/quxiaofeng/daily_planner\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Github</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"LaTeX-resources\"><a href=\"#LaTeX-resources\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"LaTeX resources\"></a>LaTeX resources</h2><h3 id=\"CTAN-LaTeX-Package\"><a href=\"#CTAN-LaTeX-Package\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"CTAN LaTeX Package\"></a>CTAN LaTeX Package</h3><ul>\n<li><p><a href=\"http://www.ctan.org/pkg/calendar\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">calendar</a> – A package for calendars and timetables</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><a href=\"http://www.ctan.org/pkg/smartdiagram\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">smartdiagram</a> - Generate diagrams from lists</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"Good-Questions-on-tex-stackexchange-com\"><a href=\"#Good-Questions-on-tex-stackexchange-com\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Good Questions on tex.stackexchange.com\"></a>Good Questions on <a href=\"http://tex.stackexchange.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">tex.stackexchange.com</a></h3><ul>\n<li><p><a href=\"http://tex.stackexchange.com/questions/36558/printing-a-double-sided-a5-document-on-a4-paper\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Printing a double-sided A5 document on A4 paper</a>    </p>\n</li>\n<li><p><a href=\"http://tex.stackexchange.com/questions/26957/how-to-make-custom-page-frame-using-latex\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">How to make custom page frame using LaTeX?</a>    </p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>similar post <a href=\"http://texblog.org/2011/04/04/make-page-margins-visible/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Making page margins visible</a>    </p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://tex.stackexchange.com/questions/45728/are-there-any-good-chinese-beamer-templates-available-for-linux-tex-live-users\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Are there any good Chinese beamer templates available for Linux TeX Live users?</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"filofax-system\"><a href=\"#filofax-system\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"filofax system\"></a>filofax system</h3><ul>\n<li><p>autofilo.sty    </p>\n</li>\n<li><p><a href=\"http://www.ctan.org/tex-archive/macros/latex/contrib/calendar\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">calendar bundle</a>    </p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"Paper-Size-Standard\"><a href=\"#Paper-Size-Standard\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Paper Size Standard\"></a><a href=\"http://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_216\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Paper Size Standard</a></h3><h2 id=\"Stationery-System\"><a href=\"#Stationery-System\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Stationery System\"></a>Stationery System</h2><h3 id=\"A5-System\"><a href=\"#A5-System\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"A5 System\"></a>A5 System</h3><ul>\n<li><p><a href=\"http://www.douban.com/photos/photo/1681928056/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">MUJI A5 2-hole Binder</a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><a href=\"http://www.muji.us/store/stationery/notebooks/tree-planting-paper-loose-leaf-a5.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">MUJI A5 loose leaf pages</a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><a href=\"http://www.douban.com/photos/photo/1681931406/#image\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">MUJI A5 Tag pages</a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Try to DIY this <a href=\"http://www.muji.us/store/stationery/notebooks/pt-paper-a5-2h-32sh-monthly.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">MUJI A5 Note MONTHLY</a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>standard two hole puncher(80mm)</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><a href=\"http://trade.taobao.com/trade/detail/tradeSnap.htm?s